original_title: Ready Up - A CS:GO Documentary by BLAST
overview: A documentary about proffesional Counter-Strike: Global Offensive by Blast Premier featuring among others Nicolai "dev1ce" Reedtz, Casper "cadiaN" Møller, and Finn "karrigan" Andersen.
tagline: It's a sport, it's a competition, it's an accidental perfect game. An absolute fight, an everyday fight, that doesn't stop. It’s Counter-Strike.
title: Ready Up - A CS:GO Documentary by BLAST
